      <div class="brand-mark">스시 김 2</div>
      <div class="brand-name">Sushi Kim <em>2</em></div>
      <p>A 30+ year Pittsburgh institution serving soulful Korean cooking and premium Japanese sushi in the heart of downtown.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Visit</h4>
      <ul>
        <li>110 Smithfield St</li>
        <li>Pittsburgh, PA 15222</li>
        <li style="margin-top: 14px"><a href="/contact">Get Directions →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Contact</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="tel:4126001000">412-600-1000</a></li>
        <li><a href="mailto:eatsushikim2@gmail.com">eatsushikim2@gmail.com</a></li>
        <li style="margin-top: 14px"><a href="/reservations">Reserve a Table →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h4>Hours</h4>
      <ul style="font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; line-height: 2;">
